    <date day="08" month="January" year="2019"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>The definition of the HTTP/2 ORIGIN frame "relaxes" the requirement
   to check DNS for various reasons.  However, experience has shown that
   such relaxation leads to security risks and is inadvisable.  This
   document restores the original requirements.</t>
    </abstract>
